---
---
<section class="section testimonials-section" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="test-header reveal">
      <div class="glow-badge">PATIENT STORIES</div>
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">Where Stories <span class="text-gradient">Became Purpose</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle text-center">
        Three patient stories from the 1990s that shattered Dr. Sharan's assumptions about medicine — and led to the founding of PRS Neurosciences in 2011.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="origin-quote">
        "We had treated the disease — but we hadn't touched the disability. We had removed the danger — but not restored the man."
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="stories-grid">
      <div class="story-card reveal">
        <div class="story-video">
          <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/2EIlftssG4vVbgtzlkY5wrZvUBw.png" alt="Story — When the Clot Was Gone But the Man Wasn't" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="play-overlay">
            <div class="play-btn">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Watch Transformation</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-info">
          <div class="story-num">Story 01</div>
          <h4 class="patient-name">When the Clot Was Gone — But the Man Wasn't</h4>
          <p class="patient-quote">"The clot has nearly dissolved!" said the young Dr. Sharan triumphantly. But the patient's son replied: "Then why is my father still not conscious? Why can't he walk? Talk? Eat?" <em>— Physical healing is not equal to functional recovery.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="story-video">
          <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/DTWiiE6hB8okbGxpoiUAEAj9Rw.png" alt="Story — When Speech Was Lost Forever" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="play-overlay">
            <div class="play-btn">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Hear the Journey</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-info">
          <div class="story-num">Story 02</div>
          <h4 class="patient-name">When Speech Was Lost Forever</h4>
          <p class="patient-quote">A young newlywed businessman. Textbook-perfect surgery. The scan showed no residual clot. Yet — he recognized no one. No comprehension. No speech. "What have we done? We had restored the body — but not the mind." <em>— The tragedy that changed everything.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="story-video">
          <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/pQKFLiDsGtejloArrfJCWiKoBHA.png" alt="Story — When a Life Saved Became a Burden" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="play-overlay">
            <div class="play-btn">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Watch This Story</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-info">
          <div class="story-num">Story 03</div>
          <h4 class="patient-name">When a Life Saved Became a Burden</h4>
          <p class="patient-quote">An unknown patient saved by emergency surgery. His wife later entered Dr. Sharan's room with fire in her voice: "Why did you save my husband's life?" <em>— What we think is medical success may not always be success for the family.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="founding-note reveal">
      <div class="fn-icon">🌱</div>
      <p>These three stories left a permanent mark. By 2011, that inner transformation took form as <strong>PRS Neurosciences and Mechatronics Research Institute</strong> — a space where the goal is not just clinical recovery, but <strong>functional restoration, human dignity, and lifetime reintegration.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    background: var(--bg-slate);
  }

  .glow-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .text-center { text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  .test-header {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .origin-quote {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(79,70,229,0.04);
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stories-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .story-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .story-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-premium);
  }

  .story-video {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .story-video img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.8s ease;
  }

  .story-card:hover .story-video img {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .play-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
    color: white;
  }

  .play-btn {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-left: 4px;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .play-btn svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }

  .story-card:hover .play-btn {
    transform: scale(1.12);
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    color: white;
  }

  .play-overlay span {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  }

  .story-info {
    padding: 28px;
  }

  .story-num {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .patient-name {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .patient-quote {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .patient-quote em {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* Founding note */
  .founding-note {
    margin-top: 56px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.1);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .fn-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .founding-note p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .founding-note strong { color: var(--text-main); }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .stories-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .section-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stories-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .founding-note { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; padding: 24px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .story-info { padding: 20px; }
  }
</style>
